==簡介==
2018年世界盃足球賽中北美洲及加勒比海區資格賽第二輪定2015年9月4日到8日舉行。由中北美洲及加勒比海足協排名第四檔次國家隊2隊和10支第一輪勝隊共12隊進行主客場二回合交手；勝隊晉級第四輪。

==Seeding==
The draw for the third round was held as part of the 2018 FIFA World Cup Preliminary Draw on 25 July 2015, starting 18:00 [[Moscow_Standard_Time|MSK]] ([[UTC+03:00|UTC+3]]), at the Konstantinovsky Palace in [[Strelna|Strelna]], [[Saint_Petersburg|Saint Petersburg]], Russia.<ref name="approval">{{cite web|url=http://www.concacaf.com/article/concacaf-to-hold-preliminary-fifa-world-cup-qualifying-draw-in-miami-on-january-15|title=CONCACAF to Hold Preliminary FIFA World Cup Qualifying Draw in Miami on January 15|publisher=CONCACAF|date=12 January 2015|access-date=2015-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121023219/http://www.concacaf.com/article/concacaf-to-hold-preliminary-fifa-world-cup-qualifying-draw-in-miami-on-january-15|archive-date=2015-01-21|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref><ref name="CONCACAF draw procedures">{{cite web|url=http://resources.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/preliminarydraw/02/66/71/11/northcentralamericacaribbean_drawprocedures_neutral.pdf|title=Draw Procedures – North, Central American & Caribbean Zone|publisher=FIFA.com|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100618/http://resources.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/preliminarydraw/02/66/71/11/northcentralamericacaribbean_drawprocedures_neutral.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

The seeding was based on the [[FIFA_World_Rankings|FIFA World Rankings]] of August 2014 (shown in parentheses).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/rank=241/concacaf.html|title=FIFA Men's Ranking – August 2014 (CONCACAF)|publisher=FIFA.com|date=14 August 2014|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210200/http://www.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/rank=241/concacaf.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> The 12 teams were seeded into two pots:
*Pot 3 contains the teams ranked 1–6.
*Pot 4 contains the teams ranked 7–12.

Each tie contained a team from Pot 1 and a team from Pot 2, with the order of legs decided by draw.

